msgid "14. Cetopariyasutta "
msgstr "14. Comprehending the Mind "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn52.14:1.1"
msgid "“Imesañca panāhaṃ, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā parasattānaṃ parapuggalānaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi—sarāgaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘sarāgaṃ cittan’ti pajānāmi … pe … avimuttaṃ vā cittaṃ ‘avimuttaṃ cittan’ti pajānāmī”ti. "
msgstr "“… And it’s because of developing and cultivating these four kinds of mindfulness meditation that I understand the minds of other beings and individuals, having comprehended them with my mind. I understand mind with greed as ‘mind with greed’ … I understand unfreed mind as ‘unfreed mind’.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
